WEBVTT


00:00:49.310 --> 00:00:52.980
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:56.060
[Episode 24]

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:04.760
What on earth is that?

00:01:04.920 --> 00:01:06.720
Crimson Moon—Goddess Genesis!

00:01:11.560 --> 00:01:12.560
Don't attack her!

00:01:14.230 --> 00:01:14.870
The skill has been unleashed.

00:01:14.870 --> 00:01:16.230
She's currently in an unkillable state.

00:01:16.230 --> 00:01:17.830
Attacking her is pointless!

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:18.530
Let me see

00:01:18.789 --> 00:01:19.400
if I can forcibly pull

00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:20.170
both of

00:01:20.230 --> 00:01:21.830
your consciousnesses back.

00:01:22.710 --> 00:01:24.590
You two must come out immediately!

00:01:24.590 --> 00:01:26.510
Yan Yuzhen has unleashed her ultimate!

00:01:26.510 --> 00:01:27.070
This could very well be

00:01:27.070 --> 00:01:28.530
a world-destroying move!

00:01:35.550 --> 00:01:36.200
No.

00:01:36.479 --> 00:01:38.229
When the boss's ultimate activates,

00:01:38.229 --> 00:01:39.680
the game state is locked.

00:01:40.039 --> 00:01:41.170
I can't do anything.

00:01:43.509 --> 00:01:44.590
Dongqing, run!

00:01:44.870 --> 00:01:46.200
Get out of this hall now!

00:01:47.789 --> 00:01:48.759
I remember now.

00:02:40.750 --> 00:02:41.350
Dongqing.

00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:43.490
Dongqing, why are you spacing out now?

00:02:43.490 --> 00:02:44.520
Get out of here now!

00:02:44.520 --> 00:02:45.010
Run!

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:46.610
Zhao Li said that

00:02:48.310 --> 00:02:49.430
when the crimson moon

00:02:49.430 --> 00:02:50.490
rises in the sky...

00:02:53.870 --> 00:02:54.750
he will return.

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:01.320
Dongqing, watch out!

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:13.600
Zhao Hengzhi!

00:03:21.470 --> 00:03:22.400
Are you alright?

00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:25.280
Do you think

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:27.280
I'm like that useless fool Situ Fei?

00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:29.190
I have so many fans.

00:03:29.960 --> 00:03:30.840
The Love Potion

00:03:31.150 --> 00:03:33.240
has drawn so much energy to me,

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:35.740
converting it into my demonic power.

00:03:36.870 --> 00:03:38.600
And you think you can defeat me?

00:03:39.630 --> 00:03:40.230
Dongqing,

00:03:41.710 --> 00:03:43.030
I can't get away.

00:03:45.030 --> 00:03:46.000
Go without me.

00:03:46.360 --> 00:03:46.750
No.

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:49.340
I will never leave you behind,

00:03:49.890 --> 00:03:51.240
nor will I leave my wife

00:03:52.030 --> 00:03:53.630
and our unborn child behind.

00:04:16.920 --> 00:04:18.160
It's over.

00:04:19.070 --> 00:04:20.000
Xia Dongqing,

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:22.430
your wife and child

00:04:23.120 --> 00:04:24.050
will come with me

00:04:24.430 --> 00:04:26.510
to my new world.

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:29.240
And you and Zhao Hengzhi

00:04:29.830 --> 00:04:32.310
will be reduced to cyber dust

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:35.310
and remain here forever.

00:04:45.630 --> 00:04:47.190
Yan Yuzhen.

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:00.720
Look,

00:05:01.630 --> 00:05:02.310
who is that?

00:05:05.480 --> 00:05:07.270
Hello, Yan Yuzhen.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:08.600
We meet again.

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:13.680
It's you.

00:05:58.510 --> 00:05:59.240
I'm fine now.

00:06:00.190 --> 00:06:01.250
Yan Yuzhen is dead.

00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:03.010
We won.

00:06:15.360 --> 00:06:17.040
Why are you all just as stubborn

00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:18.840
and inflexible as Xia Dongqing?

00:06:18.920 --> 00:06:20.320
Even the mightiest demon

00:06:20.870 --> 00:06:22.630
has a chink in its armor.

00:06:23.900 --> 00:06:24.040
♪ Listen to the rhythm of her heartbeat ♪

00:06:24.040 --> 00:06:24.560
Zhao Li!

00:06:27.470 --> 00:06:31.290
♪ Once more, I catch sight of
that familiar figure ♪

00:06:31.550 --> 00:06:35.340
♪ After a lifetime of joys and sorrows ♪

00:06:35.430 --> 00:06:35.760
Dongqing.

00:06:35.760 --> 00:06:42.300
♪ Still here, waiting for you as always ♪

00:06:47.380 --> 00:06:51.140
♪ In this world,
some farewells go unanswered ♪

00:06:51.760 --> 00:06:52.000
♪ Some linger, while others move on ♪

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:54.480
Not bad, rascal. You've got some stamina.

00:06:55.430 --> 00:06:56.080
Ya is pregnant?

00:06:56.080 --> 00:06:59.360
♪ Across vast mountains and seas ♪

00:06:59.360 --> 00:06:59.650
Ya...

00:06:59.650 --> 00:07:00.360
♪ One day ♪

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:01.270
She's fine now.

00:07:02.830 --> 00:07:03.750
Fully recovered.

00:07:03.750 --> 00:07:05.040
♪ We'll meet again ♪

00:07:05.040 --> 00:07:05.770
Take her out.

00:07:07.390 --> 00:07:08.450
Take good care of Ya

00:07:10.120 --> 00:07:11.040
and yourself.

00:07:11.300 --> 00:07:12.750
♪ Every night is ♪

00:07:12.750 --> 00:07:14.620
I'm giving your wife back to you.

00:07:14.620 --> 00:07:18.190
♪ Followed by dawn ♪

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:21.190
♪ Every farewell is ♪

00:07:22.250 --> 00:07:22.430
♪ A promise of reunion ♪

00:07:22.430 --> 00:07:23.030
Zhao Li...

00:07:25.310 --> 00:07:26.770
You've existed all along?

00:07:28.390 --> 00:07:31.000
Existed in this cyber world?

00:07:32.110 --> 00:07:33.560
Maybe. I don't know.

00:07:34.500 --> 00:07:35.670
Didn't you

00:07:35.700 --> 00:07:37.630
summon me from the void?

00:07:39.680 --> 00:07:40.240
But

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:43.080
I did tell you before that

00:07:45.120 --> 00:07:46.980
when the crimson moon appears...

00:07:50.600 --> 00:07:51.659
I'll come find you.

00:07:54.190 --> 00:07:55.590
The space is collapsing.

00:07:56.270 --> 00:07:57.450
I'm pulling your consciousnesses

00:07:57.450 --> 00:07:59.040
back into the real world right now.

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:01.070
Bring the Heavenly Maiden back
with you now.

00:08:01.070 --> 00:08:03.510
Zhao Li, Ferry Man?

00:08:06.190 --> 00:08:08.310
Zhao Hengzhi, Night Watchman.

00:08:08.760 --> 00:08:09.830
We don't look alike at all,

00:08:09.830 --> 00:08:10.270
okay?

00:08:10.870 --> 00:08:13.000
Our features may be somewhat similar,

00:08:13.090 --> 00:08:14.000
but our temperaments

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:15.240
couldn't be more different!

00:08:15.240 --> 00:08:15.640
Right.

00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:18.510
I think our vibes are different too.

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:20.190
All you ever do is slap on thick makeup

00:08:20.190 --> 00:08:21.510
and say, "It's me, Zhao Li."

00:08:21.510 --> 00:08:22.510
Is that really all you've got?

00:08:22.510 --> 00:08:23.040
What?

00:08:26.830 --> 00:08:28.430
Dongqing, we should go!

00:08:35.600 --> 00:08:36.200
Dongqing.

00:08:39.730 --> 00:08:40.360
Goodbye.

00:08:41.549 --> 00:08:42.200
Zhao Li.

00:08:49.800 --> 00:08:52.590
After that, I never saw Zhao Li again.

00:08:54.930 --> 00:08:58.310
[Five years later]

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:15.920
World War III has broken out!

00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:18.910
Han Meimei,

00:09:18.910 --> 00:09:20.440
are you trying to give me a heart attack?

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:22.170
You're a terrible shopkeeper.

00:09:22.410 --> 00:09:23.750
Sleeping in the middle of the day
like this.

00:09:23.750 --> 00:09:24.960
No wonder business is bad.

00:09:24.960 --> 00:09:25.960
What do you know?

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:27.240
It's not even

00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:28.360
peak hours yet.

00:09:30.550 --> 00:09:31.480
Uncle Dongqing,

00:09:31.550 --> 00:09:32.610
where's Sister Ya?

00:09:33.360 --> 00:09:34.890
She took Xia Yan out to play.

00:09:35.240 --> 00:09:37.240
The kid insisted on going to the zoo.

00:09:38.200 --> 00:09:39.670
Let me ask you something.

00:09:39.930 --> 00:09:41.690
Why do you call Ya "Sister,"

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:42.960
but call me "Uncle"?

00:09:43.360 --> 00:09:44.910
When will she and my nephew be back?

00:09:44.910 --> 00:09:46.150
What do you want with her?

00:09:46.150 --> 00:09:47.280
I'm not telling you.

00:09:47.630 --> 00:09:49.360
You'll know when she gets back.

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:51.670
Tell me,

00:09:51.960 --> 00:09:53.120
and I'll make you a cup of coffee.

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:54.910
I don't drink coffee, Uncle Dongqing.

00:09:54.910 --> 00:09:56.080
Are you getting old?

00:09:56.510 --> 00:09:57.840
It's been five years,
and you still don't remember it?

00:09:57.840 --> 00:10:00.040
I'll just have water. I'll help myself.

00:10:01.850 --> 00:10:02.760
Xia Dongqing,

00:10:02.790 --> 00:10:03.990
discipline your son!

00:10:04.440 --> 00:10:05.840
Daddy!

00:10:06.630 --> 00:10:07.600
My good boy!

00:10:08.030 --> 00:10:08.790
You're finally back!

00:10:08.790 --> 00:10:10.990
I'm exhausted. Next time, you take him.

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:12.410
Sister Ya, you're back.

00:10:12.790 --> 00:10:13.310
Thanks.

00:10:13.750 --> 00:10:14.910
Perfect, I was just thirsty.

00:10:14.910 --> 00:10:15.370
Tell me,

00:10:15.630 --> 00:10:16.790
did you get into trouble again

00:10:16.790 --> 00:10:17.850
and make Mommy mad?

00:10:20.360 --> 00:10:21.220
Little Xia Yan.

00:10:21.790 --> 00:10:23.030
Why haven't you said hello to her yet?

00:10:23.030 --> 00:10:24.840
Hello, Meimei.

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:26.120
I'm not doing so well.

00:10:26.120 --> 00:10:27.270
Your mom stole my water.

00:10:27.270 --> 00:10:29.200
Daddy, put me down.

00:10:29.960 --> 00:10:31.020
Go play over there.

00:10:33.760 --> 00:10:35.270
Okay, since you're both here,

00:10:35.270 --> 00:10:36.800
let's get down to business.

00:10:38.550 --> 00:10:40.000
I'm here today

00:10:40.550 --> 00:10:42.010
on behalf of someone else.

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:47.740
A wedding invitation?

00:10:47.790 --> 00:10:49.670
You and Li Lei are getting married?

00:10:49.670 --> 00:10:51.030
Who would marry him?

00:10:51.270 --> 00:10:52.870
You two have been on and off
for so many years,

00:10:52.870 --> 00:10:54.400
but aren't you still together?

00:10:54.400 --> 00:10:55.440
Why wouldn't you get married?

00:10:55.440 --> 00:10:56.510
Just playing around?

00:10:56.510 --> 00:10:57.720
Ms. Huang Shang

00:10:57.840 --> 00:10:59.000
and Mr. Zhao Hengzhi

00:10:59.030 --> 00:11:00.360
are united in marriage?

00:11:02.060 --> 00:11:03.280
[Wedding Invitation]

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:04.570
Oh, Zhao Hengzhi...

00:11:04.570 --> 00:11:05.960
[Ms. Huang Shang; Mr. Zhao Hengzhi;
United in Marriage]

00:11:05.960 --> 00:11:07.850
He doesn't answer calls
or reply to messages.

00:11:07.850 --> 00:11:09.630
He hasn't been seen for months.

00:11:09.960 --> 00:11:10.790
Now he's getting married,

00:11:10.790 --> 00:11:12.200
and he didn't even give us a heads-up?

00:11:12.200 --> 00:11:13.510
Some friend.

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:14.960
Just wait until I see him...

00:11:14.960 --> 00:11:16.150
You won't be seeing him.

00:11:16.150 --> 00:11:16.790
Why?

00:11:17.320 --> 00:11:18.720
They're not having a wedding banquet?

00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:19.150
No.

00:11:19.270 --> 00:11:21.150
He and Huang Shang have gone
to Malaysia for a trip

00:11:21.150 --> 00:11:22.030
as a sort of honeymoon.

00:11:22.030 --> 00:11:23.200
They've already left.

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:24.240
He just asked me

00:11:24.270 --> 00:11:25.530
to come and inform you.

00:11:25.670 --> 00:11:26.440
Inform you.

00:11:28.020 --> 00:11:29.720
Isn't Ms. Huang's ancestral home

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:30.670
in Malaysia?

00:11:31.550 --> 00:11:32.280
Don't tell me

00:11:32.360 --> 00:11:33.200
Zhao Hengzhi

00:11:33.750 --> 00:11:35.350
is marrying into her family?

00:11:36.270 --> 00:11:38.030
I know Huang Shang too well.

00:11:39.100 --> 00:11:40.480
She's rich and influential.

00:11:40.480 --> 00:11:41.540
And she's quite...

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:43.750
She's pretty and rich.

00:11:43.750 --> 00:11:45.000
Are you jealous of him?

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:46.260
Why would I be jealous?

00:11:46.320 --> 00:11:47.840
Easy! Easy!

00:11:48.250 --> 00:11:49.330
Mommy! Mommy!

00:11:49.360 --> 00:11:50.720
I want to play the game.

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:51.750
Well,

00:11:52.270 --> 00:11:53.440
what's so fun about this?

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:54.270
Playing that game again?

00:11:54.270 --> 00:11:55.120
Just let him play,

00:11:55.120 --> 00:11:56.450
or he'll pester us both.

00:11:56.720 --> 00:11:58.480
Catching fish, hunting birds,

00:11:58.510 --> 00:11:59.390
and building houses all day—

00:11:59.390 --> 00:12:00.870
are you training for wilderness survival?

00:12:00.870 --> 00:12:01.530
Be careful.

00:12:01.960 --> 00:12:03.150
A big tiger might

00:12:03.150 --> 00:12:04.020
suddenly jump out.

00:12:04.020 --> 00:12:04.720
Aren't you scared?

00:12:04.720 --> 00:12:06.480
There are NPCs in the game.

00:12:06.500 --> 00:12:07.630
They'll protect me.

00:12:07.650 --> 00:12:09.130
Daddy, you know nothing.

00:12:10.550 --> 00:12:11.150
Come here.

00:12:11.910 --> 00:12:12.370
Come on.

00:12:12.840 --> 00:12:13.770
Isn't this thing

00:12:13.910 --> 00:12:15.570
just like what that demon did—

00:12:15.790 --> 00:12:18.600
creating some kind of cyberspace?

00:12:18.910 --> 00:12:19.910
Watch what you're saying.

00:12:19.910 --> 00:12:21.080
Li Lei's company

00:12:21.080 --> 00:12:21.840
developed this game.

00:12:21.840 --> 00:12:22.900
It's a proper game,

00:12:23.080 --> 00:12:24.410
and it has a family mode.

00:12:24.440 --> 00:12:25.960
Aren't there three pairs of goggles?

00:12:25.960 --> 00:12:27.030
If you're worried,

00:12:27.500 --> 00:12:28.320
you and Sister Ya

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:29.520
can play with Xia Yan.

00:12:29.840 --> 00:12:30.770
I'm not playing.

00:12:31.840 --> 00:12:32.700
Suit yourself.

00:12:34.150 --> 00:12:35.080
I'm heading out.

00:12:35.270 --> 00:12:37.080
You're not staying a little longer?

00:12:37.080 --> 00:12:38.410
I have plans with Li Lei.

00:12:39.200 --> 00:12:40.800
I'm in a terrible mood today.

00:12:40.870 --> 00:12:43.270
I'm definitely breaking up with him today.

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:45.130
Then hurry up and go.

00:12:45.480 --> 00:12:47.080
Break up and then make up.

00:12:48.120 --> 00:12:49.510
Bye-bye, old man.

00:12:49.790 --> 00:12:50.850
Sister Ya, I'm off.

00:12:51.360 --> 00:12:52.240
This girl...

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:54.250
Is it on properly this time?

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:55.840
Wait,

00:12:56.820 --> 00:12:58.030
are you really playing?

00:12:58.030 --> 00:12:59.200
This is a kid's game.

00:13:00.030 --> 00:13:01.550
There aren't any customers anyway.

00:13:01.550 --> 00:13:02.550
It's family time.

00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:34.720
Daddy, Mommy, look!

00:13:34.750 --> 00:13:36.840
That's the house I built.

00:13:39.670 --> 00:13:40.670
You built it?

00:13:41.150 --> 00:13:42.080
That's amazing.

00:13:42.180 --> 00:13:42.690
Yeah.

00:13:42.720 --> 00:13:43.510
But

00:13:43.610 --> 00:13:45.090
I didn't build it alone.

00:13:45.120 --> 00:13:46.960
An uncle helped me.

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:48.480
Really?

00:13:49.030 --> 00:13:49.790
An uncle?

00:13:50.360 --> 00:13:51.020
What uncle?

00:13:52.320 --> 00:13:53.000
Dongqing.

00:13:54.670 --> 00:13:56.270
Is that a convenience store?

00:13:57.610 --> 00:13:58.470
A convenience store?

00:13:58.470 --> 00:14:02.990
[Convenience Store 444]

00:14:03.480 --> 00:14:04.550
That sign...

00:14:05.270 --> 00:14:06.790
Convenience Store 444.

00:14:10.120 --> 00:14:12.480
It's Uncle. Uncle's here.

00:14:13.320 --> 00:14:14.080
That's...

00:14:15.150 --> 00:14:16.010
That's his car.

00:14:25.750 --> 00:14:26.360
It's him.

00:14:35.390 --> 00:14:36.120
It's me,

00:14:37.030 --> 00:14:37.820
Zhao Li!

00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:40.840
The Ferry Man!

00:14:41.030 --> 00:14:42.550
I've got my big Jeep.

00:14:42.870 --> 00:14:44.990
I've got my dark-themed wardrobe.

00:14:45.080 --> 00:14:47.010
I've already slimmed back down...

00:14:47.320 --> 00:14:48.150
well, maybe not all the way back

00:14:48.150 --> 00:14:49.750
to how I looked in season one.

00:14:50.370 --> 00:14:51.720
♪ In this world,
some farewells go unanswered ♪

00:14:51.720 --> 00:14:53.580
There are some obsessions in life

00:14:53.870 --> 00:14:54.630
that we all have to let go of, right?

00:14:54.630 --> 00:14:55.910
♪ Some linger, while others move on ♪

00:14:55.910 --> 00:14:56.840
In this world,

00:14:57.840 --> 00:14:58.690
fate always finds its way back around.

00:14:58.690 --> 00:15:00.240
♪ Across vast mountains and seas ♪

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:02.170
And among the sea of people, we will

00:15:02.630 --> 00:15:02.960
♪ One day ♪

00:15:02.960 --> 00:15:05.560
ultimately meet those
we are destined to meet.

00:15:06.660 --> 00:15:10.600
♪ We'll meet again ♪

00:15:10.600 --> 00:15:11.600
Welcome to

00:15:11.600 --> 00:15:14.160
the world of Convenience Store 444.

00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:17.150
♪ Just as you looked back ♪

00:15:17.150 --> 00:15:17.950
You nutcase.

00:15:17.950 --> 00:15:20.570
♪ I opened my eyes ♪

00:15:21.250 --> 00:15:24.070
♪ Shards of time align ♪

00:15:24.090 --> 00:15:28.810
♪ Becoming eternity in that moment ♪